<h3 class="post-summary__title"><a href="https://honest-food.net/greek-lamb-shank-recipe/" data-wpel-link="internal">Greek Venison or Lamb Shanks</a></h3>
<p class="post-summary__excerpt">This is a traditional Greek lamb shank recipe done with venison shanks; the only difference between the two is venison takes longer to cook. </p>
