<div class="post-summary__content">
<p class="entry-category">Scandinavian</p>
<h3 class="post-summary__title"><a href="https://honest-food.net/tjalknol-recipe-venison/" data-wpel-link="internal">Tjalknol, Frost Bump Venison</a></h3>
<p class="post-summary__excerpt">Tjalknol is a way of cooking meat, usually venison, from frozen. It&#8217;s known as &#8216;frost bump&#8217; and involves slow cooking then brining. You eat the meat cold. </p>
</div>
</article>
