<p class="block-author-box__title">About Hank Shaw</p>
<p>Hey there. Welcome to Hunter Angler Gardener Cook, the internet&#8217;s largest source of recipes and know-how for wild foods. I am a chef, author, and yes, hunter, angler, gardener, forager and cook. Follow me on <b><a href="https://www.instagram.com/huntgathercook/" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a></b> and on <b><a href="https://facebook.com/huntgathercook/" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer">Facebook</a></b>.</p>
