<p>Loved it! And yes, I did modify it to fit our family &#8211; no nitrate salt. To stay safe I cut the roast into 1 pound slices and brined it for 2 days &#8211; the smaller hunks of meat allowed the brine to fully penetrate it in the shorter time span. Followed the rest of the recipe exactly as written. Delicious! thank you for the excellent information and guidance on cooking wild game, we appreciate you.</p>
