</div>
<p>We made this with a 2 pound sirloin roast and it came out fantastic! We omitted the cure no.1 but otherwise followed the recipe to a T. The color is notably more grey than the pink shown in the photo above,  due to the absence of cure but the color doesn&#8217;t bother us. Still tasted great. Thanks for another solid recipe!</p>
