												<b class="fn">LH</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://honest-food.net/corned-venison-recipe/comment-page-13/#comment-537817" data-wpel-link="internal"><time datetime="2025-01-22T11:11:57-08:00">January 22, 2025 at 11:11 am</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I thought the cure gave it an off putting soapy flavor, plus the propylene glycol in it is scary. It was pretty though. When I tried to slice it it was crumbly. Next time I won’t use cure. Plus I couldn’t really taste the spices at all.  I don’t know what I did wrong</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-537817" data-commentid="537817" data-postid="17948" data-belowelement="div-comment-537817" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to LH" aria-label="Reply to LH">Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
		<ol class="children">
		<li id="comment-538028" class="comment even depth-2 parent">
			<article id="div-comment-538028" class="comment-body">
				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
												<b class="fn">Tony</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://honest-food.net/corned-venison-recipe/comment-page-13/#comment-538028" data-wpel-link="internal"><time datetime="2025-01-26T20:17:58-08:00">January 26, 2025 at 8:17 pm</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Where are you getting propylene glycol in this recipe?  It&#8217;s not mentioned anywhere on the whole page.  Maybe that is your problem.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-538028" data-commentid="538028" data-postid="17948" data-belowelement="div-comment-538028" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Tony" aria-label="Reply to Tony">Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
