									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>What temp in your sous vide ? and 3hrs? Thanks</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-549965" data-commentid="549965" data-postid="17948" data-belowelement="div-comment-549965" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Grant Morris" aria-label="Reply to Grant Morris">Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
		<ol class="children">
		<li id="comment-549967" class="comment byuser comment-author-hank bypostauthor even depth-3 staff">
			<article id="div-comment-549967" class="comment-body">
				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
												<b class="fn">Hank Shaw</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://honest-food.net/corned-venison-recipe/comment-page-13/#comment-549967" data-wpel-link="internal"><time datetime="2025-11-16T11:51:50-08:00">November 16, 2025 at 11:51 am</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Grant: If I were to sous vide this, I&#8217;d do it at 145F for about 3 hours per pound of the roast.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

							</article><!-- .comment-body -->
