									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Hello Hank!  This is my first time making your recipe.  I&#8217;ve used cuts from the hind quarter/thigh.  I&#8217;m only going to cook a little when needed.  should I freeze it with the Brine or without?  Thanks!   Erin.</p>
