<div class="wp-block-group block-about__content is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<p class="is-style-heading has-huge-font-size">Hi, I&#8217;m Hank Shaw</p>
<p class="has-medium-font-size">I’m a James Beard Award-winning author and chef. I started this site back in 2007 to help you get the most out of all things wild: fish, game, edible wild plants and mushrooms. I also write <strong><a href="https://www.huntgathercook.shop/collections/all" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" data-wpel-link="exclude">cookbooks</a></strong>, and have a brand-new book out now called <strong><em><a href="https://www.huntgathercook.shop/products/borderlands-recipes-and-stories-from-the-rio-grande-to-the-pacific" data-wpel-link="exclude">Borderlands: Recipes and Stories from the Rio Grande to the Pacific</a></em></strong>. </p>
<p class="has-medium-font-size">Over on Substack, I have <strong><a href="https://tothebone.substack.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" data-wpel-link="exclude">a website dedicated to the intersection of food and nature</a></strong>. If it’s wild, you’ll find it here. Hope you enjoy the site!</p>
<div class="wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex">
