<article class="post-summary">
<div class="post-summary__image"><a href="https://honest-food.net/venison-tenderloin-recipe/" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" data-wpel-link="internal"><img width="378" height="567" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20378%20567'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-cwp_archive_lg size-cwp_archive_lg" alt="Pan seared venison tenderloin with a red wine sauce on a platter, alongside lingonberries and wild rice." data-pin-nopin="1" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 600px) 164px, 164px" decoding="async" data-lazy-srcset="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/venison-tenderloin-full-378x567.jpg 378w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/venison-tenderloin-full-276x414.jpg 276w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/venison-tenderloin-full-128x192.jpg 128w" data-lazy-src="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/venison-tenderloin-full-378x567.jpg" /><noscript><img width="378" height="567" src="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/venison-tenderloin-full-378x567.jpg" class="attachment-cwp_archive_lg size-cwp_archive_lg" alt="Pan seared venison tenderloin with a red wine sauce on a platter, alongside lingonberries and wild rice." data-pin-nopin="1" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 164px, 164px" decoding="async" srcset="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/venison-tenderloin-full-378x567.jpg 378w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/venison-tenderloin-full-276x414.jpg 276w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/venison-tenderloin-full-128x192.jpg 128w" /></noscript></a></div>
<div class="post-summary__content">
<p class="entry-category">Venison</p>
<h3 class="post-summary__title"><a href="https://honest-food.net/venison-tenderloin-recipe/" data-wpel-link="internal">Pan Seared Venison Tenderloin</a></h3>
<p class="post-summary__excerpt">A simple recipe for pan-seared venison tenderloin served with an equally simple pan sauce. Deer tenderloin is the most tender cut of the animal.</p>
</div>
</article>
<article class="post-summary">
<div class="post-summary__image"><a href="https://honest-food.net/spanish-chilindron-stew/" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" data-wpel-link="internal"><img width="378" height="398" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20378%20398'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-cwp_archive_lg size-cwp_archive_lg" alt="A bowl of chilindron, a Spanish stew." data-pin-nopin="1" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 600px) 164px, 164px" decoding="async" data-lazy-src="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/chilindron-recipe-378x398.jpg" /><noscript><img width="378" height="398" src="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/chilindron-recipe-378x398.jpg" class="attachment-cwp_archive_lg size-cwp_archive_lg" alt="A bowl of chilindron, a Spanish stew." data-pin-nopin="1" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 164px, 164px" decoding="async" /></noscript></a></div>
<div class="post-summary__content">
<p class="entry-category">Spanish</p>
<h3 class="post-summary__title"><a href="https://honest-food.net/spanish-chilindron-stew/" data-wpel-link="internal">Chilindron, Spanish Stew</a></h3>
<p class="post-summary__excerpt">Chilindron, a Spanish stew dominated by roasted red peppers, paprika and onions, is one of my favorite dishes. It&#8217;s so versatile it works with almost any meat.</p>
</div>
</article>
<article class="post-summary">
<div class="post-summary__image"><a href="https://honest-food.net/canada-goose-breast-recipe/" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" data-wpel-link="internal"><img width="378" height="567" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20378%20567'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-cwp_archive_lg size-cwp_archive_lg" alt="A simple goose breast recipe of thinly sliced Canada goose breast with rosemary and black pepper on a cutting board." data-pin-nopin="1" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 600px) 164px, 164px" decoding="async" data-lazy-srcset="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/goose-breast-recipe-378x567.jpg 378w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/goose-breast-recipe-276x414.jpg 276w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/goose-breast-recipe-128x192.jpg 128w" data-lazy-src="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/goose-breast-recipe-378x567.jpg" /><noscript><img width="378" height="567" src="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/goose-breast-recipe-378x567.jpg" class="attachment-cwp_archive_lg size-cwp_archive_lg" alt="A simple goose breast recipe of thinly sliced Canada goose breast with rosemary and black pepper on a cutting board." data-pin-nopin="1" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 164px, 164px" decoding="async" srcset="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/goose-breast-recipe-378x567.jpg 378w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/goose-breast-recipe-276x414.jpg 276w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/goose-breast-recipe-128x192.jpg 128w" /></noscript></a></div>
<div class="post-summary__content">
<p class="entry-category">Ducks and Geese</p>
<h3 class="post-summary__title"><a href="https://honest-food.net/canada-goose-breast-recipe/" data-wpel-link="internal">Seared Canada Goose Breast</a></h3>
<p class="post-summary__excerpt">This is the best Canada goose breast recipe if you want to eat it like a steak or a London broil. Reverse seared goose breast sliced thin and served simply. </p>
</div>
</article>
<article class="post-summary">
<div class="post-summary__image"><a href="https://honest-food.net/tater-tot-hotdish-venison/" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" data-wpel-link="internal"><img width="378" height="567" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20378%20567'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-cwp_archive_lg size-cwp_archive_lg" alt="A casserole dish of tater tot hotdish with a plate of the meal alongside." data-pin-nopin="1" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 600px) 164px, 164px" decoding="async" data-lazy-srcset="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/venison-hotdish-with-plate-378x567.jpg 378w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/venison-hotdish-with-plate-276x414.jpg 276w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/venison-hotdish-with-plate-128x192.jpg 128w" data-lazy-src="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/venison-hotdish-with-plate-378x567.jpg" /><noscript><img width="378" height="567" src="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/venison-hotdish-with-plate-378x567.jpg" class="attachment-cwp_archive_lg size-cwp_archive_lg" alt="A casserole dish of tater tot hotdish with a plate of the meal alongside." data-pin-nopin="1" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 164px, 164px" decoding="async" srcset="https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/venison-hotdish-with-plate-378x567.jpg 378w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/venison-hotdish-with-plate-276x414.jpg 276w, https://honest-food.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/venison-hotdish-with-plate-128x192.jpg 128w" /></noscript></a></div>
<div class="post-summary__content">
<p class="entry-category">American Recipes</p>
<h3 class="post-summary__title"><a href="https://honest-food.net/tater-tot-hotdish-venison/" data-wpel-link="internal">Tater Tot Hotdish</a></h3>
<p class="post-summary__excerpt">A classic Minnesota tater tot hotdish with options to make the mushroom soup from scratch. This is a venison hotdish, but any meat works. </p>
</div>
</article>
